title: Scott Vogel from Terror and World Be Free
itunes:title: Scott Vogel from Terror and World Be Free
description:
The damn king of hardcore returns to the podcast after a 7 year break. Scott comes on to talk about the process of keeping a band together, soul searching during COVID and being an introvert. It's always a good time hanging out with him and this is no exception. Listen and stage dive. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
